## What We're Building

A lightweight web app where designers can **prototype chatbot flows** using pre-built UI components instead of recreating the chat interface in Figma every time.

**Core Value:** Focus on conversation logic, not repetitive visual work.

---

## The Problem

Every designer recreates the VCA chat UI manually in Figma for each new flow (*Remove User*, *Manage Subscription*, etc.), causing:
- Wasted time redrawing identical components
- Inconsistent component versions across designers
- Difficulty testing realistic flows and edge cases
- Fragmented design-to-engineering handoffs

---

