## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** React + Vite + TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui component library
- **Components:** Custom VCA components from Figma (via MCP) + shadcn/ui for app shell
- **Data:** Local JSON files for flows
- **Deployment:** Standalone web app (local or shared)

**Note:** This is a design prototype. Production VCA uses Ember.js, but this sandbox prioritizes fast iteration and designer-friendly tooling. shadcn/ui provides accessible navigation and layout components, while VCA chat components are custom-built from Figma.

